title: Snow Monkeys in Hot Springs
description: A group of Japanese macaques, also known as snow monkeys, relaxing in a hot spring surrounded by snow. The focus is on one monkey with a distinctive pink face and hands, sitting on a rock at the edge of the water, while others are seen in the background.

title: Water Cycle Illustration
description: An illustration depicting the water cycle. The sun is shining in the upper corner, with arrows indicating the movement of water vapor rising from the ocean, forming clouds, and precipitating as rain or snow on the mountains. The landscape features lush green forests and a river flowing down from the mountains into the ocean.

title: Frog Among Eggs
description: A close-up image of a frog surrounded by its eggs in a watery environment. The frog has a brownish coloration with prominent eyes, and the eggs are visible as translucent spheres with dark centers, floating among green aquatic plants.

title: Fresh Leaves with Raindrops
description: A close-up image of a branch with fresh green leaves. The leaves are vibrant and glistening with raindrops, showcasing the beauty of nature after rainfall. The background is softly blurred, emphasizing the leaves and droplets.
